Installation Instructions
*************************

Build Dependencies
==================

- clang with C++11
- libc++
- pkg-config
- `xdrpp` built with libc++

`xdrpp` can be found at: http://www.scs.stanford.edu/~dm/repos/xdrpp.git. Make
sure to build it using libc++. You can install `xdrpp` using `make install` or
keep a copy in this directory or its parent.

Basic Installation
==================

  1. Type `./autogen.sh`.
  2. Type `./configure && make`.
  3. Type `make install` to install.
